reviewText: I am rating this DVD with one star, not because it was a bad product, but because Dalton Kehoe is the most boring person alive. Unless you want to fall asleep easily, I would not recommend this to anyone unless I did not like them.
Kehoe lectures great! Gives good illustrations and covers the basics.  Loved the lecture! Listening got me inspired to learn more about communication.
I gave this as a gift to someone that just became a manager, and he told me that he loved it. that It has helped him tremendously, and that he highly recomends it
